                        the left (e.g. <locus target="#6va">6va</locus>, 6vb, 11va,
                        12va)<!--The names of this hands need to be replaced by appropriate refs.--></handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h4" script="Ethiopic"> - the crux ansata with coronis on
                           <locus target="#14v">14v</locus>.<!--The names of this hands need to be replaced by appropriate refs.--></handNote>
